      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>black beans</strong> with a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a<strong> baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 6-7 min or until the beans pop – these are your <strong>popped beans</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> remaining black beans</strong> to the pan with the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, mix everything together and cook for 2 min further</p>",
      "order": 5,
