    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Make 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> wells in the pan and crack the <strong>eggs</strong> into them, then cook covered for 2-3 min or until the eggs are done to your liking – this is your <strong>fajita-spiced shakshuka</strong></p>",
