    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the eggs are cooking, cut the <strong>avocado<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>in half lengthways, around the <strong>stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Remove the <strong>stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh </strong>and slice finely lengthways</p>",
