      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> fajita-spiced shakshuka</strong> with the <strong>sliced avocado</strong> to the side</p><p>Top with the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>popped beans</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
